1.01	The_Search_(DS9_episode)	The Search (Star Trek: Deep Space Nine)	"The Search" is the title of a two-part episode of Star Trek: Deep Space Nine, the first and second episodes of the third season, the 47th and 48th episodes overall. It marks the first appearance of the starship USS Defiant, which plays a large role throughout the rest of the series. It also marks the first appearance of the redesigned communicator badge.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b7/STDS9Ep301.jpg/270px-STDS9Ep301.jpg
